<div
    class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-[#E8E2D9] text-center w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto"
>
    {/* 1レッスンあたりの料金 */}
    <div class="mb-6 font-serif text-[#544A40]">
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg tracking-widest text-[#544A40]">
            ― 1レッスンあたりの料金 ―
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center items-stretch gap-0">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 py-2 min-w-[90px] md:min-w-[120px]"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#A88B58] mb-1 font-medium"
                    >30分</span
                >
                <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center">
                    <span
                        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                        >5,000</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#544A40] ml-0.5 font-bold"
                        >円</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 py-2 min-w-[90px] md:min-w-[120px] border-x border-[#E8E2D9]"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#A88B58] mb-1 font-medium"
                    >45分</span
                >
                <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center">
                    <span
                        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                        >7,500</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#544A40] ml-0.5 font-bold"
                        >円</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 py-2 min-w-[90px] md:min-w-[120px]"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#A88B58] mb-1 font-medium"
                    >60分</span
                >
                <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center">
                    <span
                        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                        >10,000</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#544A40] ml-0.5 font-bold"
                        >円</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {/* 月謝の目安 */}
    <div class="pt-6 border-t border-[#E8E2D9]">
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg tracking-widest text-[#544A40] font-serif">
            ― 月謝の目安 ―
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center items-stretch gap-2 md:gap-0">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 max-w-xs mx-auto md:mx-0 md:pr-8"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-xs md:text-base text-[#A88B58] mb-1 font-medium"
                    >30分 × 月3回</span
                >
                <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center">
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                        >15,000</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#544A40] ml-0.5 font-bold"
                        >円</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 max-w-xs mx-auto md:mx-0 border-l border-[#E8E2D9] md:pl-8"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-xs md:text-base text-[#A88B58] mb-1 font-medium"
                    >60分 × 月2回</span
                >
                <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center">
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                        >20,000</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#544A40] ml-0.5 font-bold"
                        >円</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-[#6B5F54]/70">
            ※別途教材費がかかる場合がございます。
        </p>
    </div>

    {/* 補足情報 */}
    <div
        class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#E8E2D9] text-sm text-[#6B5F54] space-y-1"
    >
        <p>入会金：<span class="font-medium text-[#544A40]">無料</span></p>
        <p>
            出張費・交通費：<span class="font-medium text-[#544A40]"
                >レッスン料金に含まれます</span
            >
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs opacity-70 pt-2">
            <span class="inline-block">※ご希望に合わせて、</span><span
                class="inline-block">月1回〜4回まで</span
            ><span class="inline-block">受講頻度をお選びいただけます。</span>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
